Interface IndoorGardenImplementationI

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndoorGardenCI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndoorGarden, IndoorGardenConnector, IndoorGardenInboundPort, IndoorGardenOutboundPort

    public interface IndoorGardenImplementationI
    The interface IndoorGardenImplementationI defines the methods that an indoor garden must implement for its services.

    Invariant

     invariant       true        // no invariant
